g.title: user
g.text: PK UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT uuid_generate_v4()
TEXT CHECK (role IN ('Worker','Employer','Support','Finance','Admin','Super Admin')) NOT NULL

g.title: worker
g.text: PK UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT uuid_generate_v4()
UUID UNIQUE REFERENCES "user"(id) ON DELETE CASCADE

g.title: facility
g.text: PK UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT uuid_generate_v4()

g.title: shift
g.text: PK UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT uuid_generate_v4()
UUID REFERENCES worker(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
UUID REFERENCES facility(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
INT GENERATED ALWAYS AS (EXTRACT(DAY FROM (end_date - start_date)) / 7 + 1) STORED
